Classification: Reality
Status: New Series
Network: Syfy ( USA)
Airs: Tuesdays at 10:30 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: October 30, 2012
(http://www.tvrage.com/shows/id-31508)

Each week two new teams get four days and a shoe-string budget to create a video that best captures that week's theme. These talented guys and gals will have to dig deep into their bag of viral tricks and put their editing, writing and acting skills to the ultimate test. The pressure is on as they work hard to impress an expert panel of viral video judges
